data.name: CreateDashboardStagingPriority4
ReadCaseCaseAssignmentServiceProvider
data.value: select * from ( select T1.NUMB, T1.NO_JURISDICTION_CD, T2.EFFECTIVE_DATE, T2.DISCONTINUE_DATE, T2.CREATED_TIMESTAMP, T2.SPD_ID, T2.OFF_ID, T2.OSP_CODE, T2.OSP_DATE from CKT_CASE T1 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_ASSIGN_CASE T2 with(readuncommitted) on T1.NO_JURISDICTION_CD = ' ' and T1.NUMB = T2.CAS_NO and T2.EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @effectiveDate and T2.DISCONTINUE_DATE >= @effectiveDate and T1.NUMB > @numb ) S1 outer apply ( select top(1) SERVICE_PRVDER_ID, USER_ID from CKT_SERVICE_PRVDER where SERVICE_PRVDER_ID = S1.SPD_ID ) S2 order by S1.NUMB
